  %p== #{popup_link_to 'Women’s Empowerment Principle 7', 'http://weprinciples.org/Site/Principle7/'} highlights the importance of using sex-disaggregated data to measure and report on progress. These gender related COP Self-Assessment questions encourage and support companies to report on their progress towards implementing the Women’s Empowerment Principles. The final question on sex-disaggregated data refers to data that is collected and presented separately on women and men. It is quantitative statistical information on the differences and inequalities between men and women.
